Program: The Documentary
Title: A New Home in Germany
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03cc8w4
Last Broadcast Date: New Year's Day 2016
Having arrived in Germany, the Dhnie family's dramatic journey to their new home may be over, but the difficulties of adjusting to a new life are just beginning. Alma hopes Europe will provide her with more independence, Abean desperately wants to be allowed to go to school, and the whole family faces the challenge of learning German whilst living on a basketball court packed full of refugees. (Photo: The Dhnie family Credit: Manveen Rana) Show less